dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents the locations of the major cities (with populations) of the world at a scale of 1:15,000,000. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.World Cities provides a base map layer of the cities for the world. The cities include national capitals, provincial capitals, major population centers, and landmark cities.
